{"id": 596, "genre": 1000, "title": "《小王子》上映，这些刻奇的句子又要刷屏了", "description": "除了“哦”，你还能回复它们什么？", "record_count": 4655, "comment_count": 60, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160608143621wR6z2TU10l97JZh8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-26T01:36:14Z", "questions": [{"id": 495, "title": "《小王子》上映，这些刻奇的句子又要刷屏了", "content": "《小王子》上映，这些刻奇的句子又要刷屏了", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 19614, "content": "“如果你想要制造羁绊，就得承受流泪的风险。”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194039fpm0u8ZAr1FBTwNP.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19616, "content": "“所有的大人都曾经是小孩，虽然，只有少数的人记得。”", "image": "img/option/option/201606071934076v5DFfEqYMsL2e7i.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19617, "content": "“一旦你驯服了什么，就要对TA负责，永远的负责。”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193407wpZRG85XO0MAQgHK.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19621, "content": "“我太年轻了，甚至不懂怎么去爱她。”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193407BxRJMPHOzdZIXU2V.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19619, "content": "“也许世界上也有五千朵和你一模一样的花，但只有你是我独一无二的玫瑰。”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194039rTqkCLVBgyo8DvpE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19620, "content": "“当一个人情绪低落的时候，他会格外喜欢看日落。”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193408N3f0GYs4KZRD158S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19622, "content": "“只有用心灵才能看得清事物本质，真正重要的东西是肉眼无法看见的。”", "image": "img/option/option/201606071940393ceKB1lqCyPNTtsO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19625, "content": "“时间会缓和所有悲伤，当你的悲伤被安抚以后，你会因为认识过我而感到满足。”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193408xjQ4VFyf29dOu6tX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 19624, "content": "易烊千玺的配音真的很不错。", "image": "img/option/option/20160608143427pQz1NZtS72KuFYDq.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}